msgctxt "1348"
msgid "Businesswoman"
msgstr "Empesaria"

msgctxt "1352"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "1356"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "68_Businesswoman"
msgid "I saw a bunch of rough-looking men heading over to Theater Square Earlier. I'm pretty sure they were yakuza."
msgstr "Vi varios tipos yendo a la Plaza del Teatro. Estoy bastante segura de que eran yakuzas."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Excuse me, miss? You didn't happen to see some shady-looking guys roll through here a while ago, did you? I'm talking yakuza types."
msgstr "Disculpe, señorita. ¿No vio a algunos tipos sospechosos pasar por aquí? Probablemente yakuzas."

msgctxt "104_Businesswoman"
msgid "Oh, I did! I'm pretty sure they were headed towards Theater Square."
msgstr "¡Ah, sí! Estoy segura de que se fueron a la Plaza del Teatro."

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "Really? Thanks!"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¡Gracias!"

msgctxt "128_Businesswoman"
msgid "Of course. Good luck..."
msgstr "Claro. Buena suerte..."

